tip.text: Great ambience and service, loved the fresh tomato salad from Cordoba. The pork was great. The olive oil cake and Cordoba cake was awesome!!!
Excellent service and great food! Do ask for rooftop seats! We went with the recommendations of the waiter and had a great time. The olive oil cake with PX liquor jelly, the Cordoba cake was super!
Karage was awesome! Great quality all round!

Highly recommended! Chefs and service staff are all from 6 star hotels in Singapore, and the price is super reasonable! The Peking roast duck, homemade beancurd with charcoal powder, lotus root soup..
